title: Vaccination: Are we there yet?
description:
Why do we vaccinate? This video shows how vaccinations have helped eliminate certain vaccine preventable diseases in Canada. Get the facts: http://bit.ly/hcdnsIV

The accessible version of this video can be found at:
http://www.healthycanadians.gc.ca/video/vaccines-vaccination-eng.php
